{"tid":2029090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克議長獲參議院力撐訪台","createTime":"2020-05-22T05:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:01:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"85d89be9d485f4cc121506027d5fa7a5d364503e","tid":2029090,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200522/GPP4RJ233YQWULKY7V5GPA62XA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200522%2FGPP4RJ233YQWULKY7V5GPA62XA%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=ca97943c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200522%2FGPP4RJ233YQWULKY7V5GPA62XA%2F&h=a340412e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200522/GPP4RJ233YQWULKY7V5GPA62XA/</a><br />\n<br />\n捷克議長獲參議院力撐訪台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200522/large/1590074951_bd04.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200522%2Flarge%2F1590074951_bd04.gif&h=8e1d9c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捷克參議院支持議長維特齊訪台。<br />\n<br />\n捷克參議院周三以50比1壓倒性票數通過決議，指中國威脅不要訪台是對捷克內政的干涉，支持議長維特齊率團訪問台灣。無黨籍參議員賀社表示，捷克是一個獨立、自由和民主的國家，不該被其他國家勒索，尤其是獨裁國家。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蔡英文任內購近千億美軍備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轟華干涉別國內政<br />\n<br />\n參議院前議長柯佳洛（Jaroslav Kubera）原定今年2月訪台，惟出發前猝死。一封由中國大使館署名、威脅他訪台將對捷克企業報復的信經傳媒披露後震驚捷克政壇，總統、總理等政府高層3月。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n決議案中還指出，捷克國會議員訪問台灣符合捷克長。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n柯佳洛的繼任者維特齊尚未決定訪台，不過，他對中國大使館針對台灣一再施壓感不滿。他前日指：「如果中國指使捷克。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n維特齊指出，中國大使館官員日前打電話到辦公室，警告他不要祝賀台灣總統就職，在他還沒決定前就對他下令，讓他感到荒謬和難以。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"d37d2979abeff2366ebcf5fdc6ddc7586838d9ce","tid":2029090,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}